Super Eagles superstar, Ahmed Musa has celebrated his son on social media as the young boy one year old. The Super Eagles superstar, Ahmed Musa, has celebrated his son’s birthday as the young child turns one year old. An elated Musa took to his Instagram page to celebrate his boy. Sharing photos on his page, he wrote a beautiful caption, wishing his son ‘sweet memories’. He wrote: “May your Birthday, bring loads of joyful and sweet memories in your life.“May you have a great and successful year ahead. Happy Birthday Son.” Below are more photos Musa shared of his son: Source